    "body": "I think that currently the only one is error 1180 from SMT checker. Check out [the command-line test `standard_model_checker_invariants_contract`](https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/tree/develop/test/cmdlineTests/standard_model_checker_invariants_contract).\r\n\r\nWe do plan to use it more and maybe convert some of the existing warnings into `info` messages but this has been a low priority so far. May take some time until we focus specifically on that unless this comes up in one of the features we're currently adding or someone explicitly requests some warning to be demoted.",
